2.12	Langley%2C_British_Columbia_(district_municipality)	Langley, British Columbia (district municipality)	The Township of Langley is a district municipality immediately east of the City of Surrey in southwestern British Columbia, Canada. It extends south from the Fraser River to the U.S. border, and west of the City of Abbotsford. Langley Township is not to be confused with the City of Langley, which is adjacent to the township but politically is a separate entity.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/96/Flag_of_Langley%2C_British_Columbia.svg/100px-Flag_of_Langley%2C_British_Columbia.svg.png
